column8: Cloudy. Very high (95%) chance of rain. The chance of a thunderstorm. Light winds becoming northerly 20 to 25 km/h in the late evening.

Cloudy. Very high (95%) chance of rain, most likely in the morning and afternoon. The chance of a thunderstorm, possibly severe with damaging winds and large hail in the afternoon and early evening. Possible heavy falls in the afternoon and early evening. Winds northwesterly 30 to 40 km/h increasing to 35 to 50 km/h before dawn then becoming light in the evening.
Partly cloudy. Medium (50%) chance of showers, most likely in the morning and afternoon. The chance of fog in the early morning. Light winds.
Partly cloudy. Winds southeast to southwesterly 15 to 20 km/h tending west to northwesterly during the morning then shifting east to southeasterly during the afternoon.
Partly cloudy. Winds easterly 15 to 20 km/h turning northerly 15 to 25 km/h during the morning.
Partly cloudy. Slight (30%) chance of a shower. Winds north to northwesterly 20 to 30 km/h.
Partly cloudy. High (70%) chance of showers. Winds north to northwesterly 25 to 40 km/h.
Cloudy. Very high (95%) chance of showers. Winds northerly 40 to 50 km/h turning northwesterly 30 to 40 km/h later.
